# Announcing Your Giveaway

When your giveaway is ready, follow these steps:

## Announce the Giveaway on Twitter once a week for 3 weeks

Tweet your announcement with a direct link to the giveaway site and use at least these hastags:

```
#Kindle 
#KindleGiveaway
#AmazonKDP 
#ebook 
#bookbuzzr 
#bookgiveaway 
#kindlebargain 
#freekindlereads
```
